===索思沃尔德===
{{main|索思沃尔德圣爱德门堂}}
另一个宏伟的萨福克郡教堂是[[索思沃尔德|索思沃尔德]]的圣爱德门堂（St Edmund's Church,），保留了中世纪的圣坛屏饰<ref>[http://www.suffolkchurches.co.uk/Southwold.htm St. Edmund, Southwold, photos, suffolkchurches.co.uk]</ref>。

===考斯顿===
诺福克郡考斯顿的圣亚革尼斯堂（St. Agnes' Church）也被称为“羊毛教堂”。其十五世纪的中殿和西侧钟楼由萨福克伯爵迈克尔·德拉波尔资助。他通过羊毛生意致富。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cawstonparish.info/wollenindustry.htm |title=St. Agnes' Church at Cawston |author=|date=2016 |website=Cawston Parish at Norfolk - UK |publisher=Cawston Parish at Norfolk - UK |access-date=April 25, 2016 |quote=a wool church being financed and built by Michael de la Pole, 2nd Earl of Suffolk and Catherine his wife (with the exception of the north aisle built by Robert Oxburgh) displaying wealth which he gained from the woollen Industry}}</ref>作为典型的“羊毛教堂”，圣亚革尼斯堂的规模远比普通的中世纪村庄所需要的要宏伟得多。萨福克伯爵不遗余力地美化内部：入口上方的雕刻；[[法国|法国]]石料用于钟楼和中殿；屋顶虽然还是典型的木制东盎格利亚风格，但是精心设计了弯曲的梁，三位天使伸出翅膀盘旋<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=HrzPlqLjR1MC&pg=PA246&dq=%22wool+church%22+suffolk&ei=k4TxSP2cJZH2sQP6muHZBg&sig=ACfU3U26XYpiGOspGHf5SqlsRNYOaxuN6gA World History of Architecture, Marian Moffett, Michael Fazio, Lawrence Wodehouse, McGraw-Hill Professional, New York, 2003]</ref>。

显然，在中世纪的东盎格利亚，绵羊为建筑赎罪提供了货币。

===伊普斯威奇圣革利免堂===
[[伊普斯威奇圣革利免堂|伊普斯威奇圣革利免堂]]的资金主要来自[[伊普斯威奇|伊普斯威奇]]港口的羊毛贸易。钟楼，是由富有的羊毛商人捐款建造的。<ref name="Ipswich Icons">{{cite news |title=Ipswich Icons: Can a new use be found for abandoned medieval church? |url=https://www.ipswichstar.co.uk/news/ipswich-icons-st-clements-church-1-5584708 |work=Ipswich Star |issue=30 June 2018 |publisher=Archant Community Media Ltd |date=2018 |language=en}}</ref>

